close_reason: Source/tests/docs lane complete; concrete findings are fixed where scoped to this PR or tracked as open backlog.
body: Execution lane for specialized repository-surface inspection. No code edits; report missing or weakly tracked work as candidate pm items with canonical parent suggestions.
